This application has been created for the sole purpose of tracking students attendance.

At the start of the application, you had to enter in your basic details.
In order to successful track your attendance, you need to Check in and Check out by clicking on the Red Button.
However, this can only be achieved by first entering in the module code that you are checking into,
Secondly, you need to ensure that your location settings are on and that you are at your designated venue.
Once you have checked in you may close the application and return to it when your Lecture is complete and check out.
You will receive a notifications welcoming you to your venue and to remind you to checkout once you have checked in.

You may also view your own attendance report by selecting the report tab.
All your details will be sent to the administrative office for verification.

If there are any issues, please consult your lecturer.